# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

What in the music?

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

The project will focus on playing music for the user. The user will be free to choose genre and song, or even get a random combination.

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

The software will give the user a few paths. He can choose to listen to music from 3 to 5 music genres. In each genre, there will be about 5 songs. If the user is not sure about what music to listen to, he can ask to software to summarize a genre for him and then he can decide if that works for him or not. If not, then he can ask the software to describe another genre and if he likes that, he can tell it to play a random song from there.

